Feature: Admin manage collaborators
  An Admin can create collaborators
  When a user request to become a collaborator
  Admin can deny or accept the user request
  An Admin can cancel collaborator or user account when its necessary

  Background: As an Admin

  Scenario: I should be able to create a collaborator account

  Scenario: I have the ability to accept a user request to become a collaborator

  Scenario: I have the ability to deny a user request to become a collaborator

  Scenario: I have the ability to cancel a collaborator account

  Scenario: I have the ability to cancel a user account
